Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Car sales slump
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w2m4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 May 1980
Massive slump in US-made car sales signals recession is biting. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.